                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_QyV6UK": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Garments in the archive are crafted as one-of-a-kind couture pieces, often designed for lookbooks, exhibitions, or artistic collaborations. While not available for direct sale, inquiries from collectors or institutions are considered thoughtfully.<\/p>",
